Accompanied by a side of roasted herb potatoes and a medley of seasonal vegetables, topped with a rich, savory glaze."}, {"id": 14, "name": "Patriot's Prime Ribeye", "price": 55.0, "cost_price": 27.5, "description": "A succulent ribeye steak, dry-aged for 28 days, seared to perfection, and served with a side of garlic butter mushrooms and truffle-infused mashed potatoes."}, {"id": 15, "name": "American Fusion Tofu Scramble", "price": 19.0, "cost_price": 9.5, "description": "A bold fusion of flavors with seasoned tofu, saut\u00e9ed kale, red bell peppers, and black beans, topped with sliced avocado and vegan cheese, accompanied by gluten-free toast."}, {"id": 16, "name": "Garden-Fresh Vegan Pizza", "price": 21.0, "cost_price": 10.5, "description": "A thin, crispy gluten-free crust topped with our signature tomato sauce, a mix of vegan mozzarella and cheddar, and a garden's bounty of fresh vegetables, including bell peppers, mushrooms, and artichokes."}, {"id": 17, "name": "Independence Portobello Burger", "price": 26.0, "cost_price": 13.0, "description": "A premium vegan burger featuring a large grilled Portobello mushroom cap, topped with roasted red peppers, vegan pesto aioli, and arugula, served on a toasted artisanal bun."}, {"id": 18, "name": "Freedom Chocolate Lava Cake", "price": 12.0, "cost_price": 6.0, "description": "An indulgent gluten-free chocolate cake with a molten chocolate center, served warm with a dusting of powdered sugar and a side of dairy-free vanilla ice cream."}]
